'''玛丽亚·埃莱娜·贝罗'''（{{lang-en|Maria Elena Bello}}，{{bd|1967年|4月18日|catIdx=B}}）是一位美国女演员和作家。曾参与过《[[暴力效應|暴力效應]]》（2005年）， 《[[感谢你抽烟_(电影)|感谢你抽烟]]》（2006）等电影的演出。电视方面，她曾在NBC剧集《[[仁心仁術|仁心仁術]]》中扮演Anna Del Amico医生（1997年–1998年），2013年与[[基夫·修打蘭|基夫·修打蘭]]合作了[[福克斯廣播公司|Fox]]电视剧《[[触摸未来|触摸未来]]》。

==早期生活==
贝罗出生于[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]][[诺里斯敦_(宾夕法尼亚州)|諾里斯敦]]。<ref name=filmref>{{cite web | url = http://www.filmreference.com/film/63/Maria-Bello.html | title = Maria Bello Biography (1967-) | publisher = FilmReference.com | accessdate = 2013-12-02 | archive-date = 2013-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203093346/http://www.filmreference.com/film/63/Maria-Bello.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ematrimony.org/priestscorner/20060127_belloquote_rickey.htm |title=Supporting, Encouraging and Challenging the WWME Community |publisher=eMatrimony |date= |accessdate=2013-12-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130926195102/http://www.ematrimony.org/priestscorner/20060127_belloquote_rickey.htm |archivedate=2013年9月26日 }}</ref>她的父亲是[[意大利裔美国人|意大利裔美国人]]，来自[[意大利|意大利]][[蒙泰拉|蒙泰拉]]，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://napoli.repubblica.it/cronaca/2012/07/01/news/all_attrice_maria_bello_l_ischia_humanitarian_award-38334552/ |title=All'attrice Maria Bello l'Ischia Humanitarian Award / Actress Maria Bello: Ischia Humanitarian Award |publisher=Napoli.repubblica.it |date= |accessdate=2013-12-02 |quote=Il nonni paterni di Maria Bello, 45 anni, erano originari di Montella, in provincia di Avellino / The paternal grandparents of Maria Bello, 45, were from Montella, Avellino |archive-date=2013-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204193049/http://napoli.repubblica.it/cronaca/2012/07/01/news/all_attrice_maria_bello_l_ischia_humanitarian_award-38334552/ |dead-url=no }} (in Italian)</ref>母亲是波兰裔美国人。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/10/AR2006081000437.html |title=Maria Bello, 'Getting Better and Better' |publisher=Washingtonpost.com |date=2006-08-11 |accessdate=2013-12-02 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021074138/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/10/AR2006081000437.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>她成长于一个工薪阶层的[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]家庭，毕业于约翰·卡罗尔大主教高中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800019251/bio|title=Maria Bello|work=[[Yahoo!_Movies|Yahoo! Movies]]|accessdate=2010-06-24|archive-date=2011-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622004831/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800019251/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.askmen.com/celebs/women/actress_250/258_maria_bello.html|title=Maria Bello|work=[[AskMen.com|AskMen.com]]|accessdate=2010-06-24|archive-date=2010-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100119035735/http://www.askmen.com/celebs/women/actress_250/258_maria_bello.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

后来，她在[[维拉诺瓦大学|维拉诺瓦大学]]主修[[政治学|政治学]]。这时开始上表演课，毕业后，她参与一些纽约的戏剧作品表演来磨练演技。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/263285/Maria-Bello/biography "Maria Bello"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/263285/Maria-Bello/biography |date=20140714205027 }}, NYTimes.com</ref>

